      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ACOUSTIC BUBBLES (7) jumped favourite at Geraldton prior to the break when beaten 3.3L going straight to 1400m. The form out of her last start worked out well and she's won at the trials coming into this. Should get every chance close to the speed and a forward showing is expected. WATERSHED WISDOM (8) gets the blinkers on for the first time today after tiring from the front over 1232m last start. She drops back in trip today and the stable's strike jockey hops on board. Draws nicely again here and she can make an impression. MISS BANOFFEE (6) landed midfield on debut here and never really featured, finishing 4.6L off the winner. She'd trialled well coming into her debut though and she'll be better for the debut run. Can feature. LE BEAU (1) won't be far away if he runs up to recent form. RIVER BEAUTY (3) comes back in trip today and finds a suitable race.",
